//   - Formspree (https://formspree.io): replace action URL below
//   - Netlify Forms: add data-netlify="true" to the form element
//   - Custom API endpoint: update FORM_ENDPOINT below and implement handler
//   - Airtable / Google Sheets via Zapier/Make: connect via webhook URL
//
// Current behavior: The form shows a success state via JS on submit.
// No data is sent until a real endpoint is configured.
//
